PromptTemplate: Which countries share a land border with {subject_entity}? Answer None if there are no land borders.
In which city did {subject_entity} die? Answer None if {subject_entity} is still alive. There is at most one city possible.
How many episodes does the series {subject_entity} have? Answer with a single number.
Who won the {subject_entity}? If you do not know you can guess.
Where do shares of {subject_entity} trade? Answer None if it is not traded. At most one answer is possible.
